      <lg n="1" type="stanza"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-954-0852-line-1"><hi rend="display-initial">O</hi>N rainy Days alone I dine,</l><l n="2" xml:id="spp-954-0852-line-2"> Upon a Chick, and Pint of Wine.</l><l n="3" xml:id="spp-954-0852-line-3"> On rainy Days I dine alone,</l><l n="4" xml:id="spp-954-0852-line-4"> And pick my Chicken to the Bone:</l><l n="5" xml:id="spp-954-0852-line-5"> But this my Servants much enrages,</l><l n="6" xml:id="spp-954-0852-line-6"> No Scraps remain to save Board-wages.</l><l n="7" xml:id="spp-954-0852-line-7"> In Weather fine I nothing spend,</l><l n="8" xml:id="spp-954-0852-line-8"> But often spunge upon a Friend:</l><l n="9" xml:id="spp-954-0852-line-9"> Yet where He's not so rich as I,</l><l n="10" xml:id="spp-954-0852-line-10"> I pay my Club, and so G<hi rend="SMALL-CAPS">OD</hi> b'y'────.954-0852   </l></lg></div>
